  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Application
    The main application model object that represents the whole application.
    Home<T extends Entity>
    Una home representa la interfaz hacia el lugar físico donde se persisten los objetos.
    IModel<T>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAutogeneratedIdHome<T extends Entity>
    Base Home implementation for reusing the code to generate id's, and between CollectionBasedHome.
    CollectionBasedHome<T extends Entity>
    Implementación de Home que mantiene los objetos en memoria, dentro de una collection.
    Entity
    Base class for all domain objects.
    Model<T> Deprecated
    Este model la verdad que no me cierra ni un poco.
    ObjectSet
    An object set executes a given persistence-initialization logic on an Application object.
    ObservableObject
    Base class for observable objects.
    ObservableUtils
    Utility class for Observable object functions, for example to force triggering a property change method.
    Property
    The Property class reifies an observable property in a model.
    ScalaBeanInfo  
    Search<T>
    Base class for implementing search objects.
    SearchByExample<T extends Entity>
    Default implementation of a Search, delegating into a Home object and performing a search by example.
